data.description: Wonderful, fully updated home in the sought after community of Shadow Moss. New flooring throughout, upgraded fixtures and bathrooms. Spacious, open living area makes everyday living/entertaining simple. Lots of counter and cabinet space in the kitchen that open to the main living area with dining area off to the side. Guest bedrooms are located along the front side of the house with great closet space and updated guest bathroom with tub/shower combo. Owners suite features walk-in closet and oversized bathroom. Spacious laundry room and 2 car attached garage, fully fenced in yard with grilling concrete patio. A must see home!
